thread.title: BRIEF-Guangdong Zhengye Technology sees FY 2018 Q1 net profit up 30 pct to 60 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Guangdong Zhengye Technology sees FY 2018 Q1 net profit up 30 pct to 60 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - guangdong zhengye technology co ltd

text:
Feb 23 (Reuters) - Guangdong Zhengye Technology Co Ltd
* Says it sees FY 2018 Q1 net profit to increase by 30 percent to 60 percent, or to be 28.2 million yuan to 34.6 million yuan
* Says FY 2017 Q1 net profit was 21.7 million yuan
* Comments that increased automation equipment sales and profit of units as main reasons for the forecast
